Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Breaks: ppsspp-common (<< 1.1.1-r93.f4.p3.l1635.a161.t83~37~), ppsspp-qt (<< 1.1.1-r93.f4.p3.l1635.a161.t83~37~), ppsspp-sdl (<< 1.1.1-r93.f4.p3.l1635.a161.t83~31~)
